---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="Moveroo | Privacy Policy"
	description="Learn how Moveroo Australia protects your personal information and manages data responsibly in accordance with the Privacy Act 1988."
	canonical="https://moveroo.com.au/privacy-policy/"
>
	<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-slate-50 to-slate-100 py-24">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
			<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-emerald-600">Privacy Policy</p>
			<h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Protecting your personal information</h1>
			<p class="mt-6 text-base text-slate-600">
				Moveroo Australia is committed to safeguarding your privacy and managing your personal information responsibly. The policy below summarises how we collect, use, store and protect your data in line with the <em>Privacy Act 1988 (Cth)</em>.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="bg-white py-20">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-12 px-6 text-slate-600">
			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Information we collect</h2>
				<p>
					We may request basic identifying details—such as your name, email address, phone number or postal address—when you submit enquiries,
					request quotes or participate in promotions. We do <strong>not</strong> seek sensitive information like your religious beliefs, health details,
					or criminal history.
				</p>
				<p>
					From time to time, we may run surveys or gather feedback to improve our services. Participation is optional.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Cookies and website usage</h2>
				<p>
					Moveroo uses cookies to remember preferences and streamline your browsing experience. Cookies do not identify you personally but can
					make return visits more convenient. You can disable cookies in your browser settings; however, this may limit certain website features.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Providing personal information</h2>
				<p>
					Sharing your personal information with us is voluntary. When you do, you consent to Moveroo collecting, storing and using it according to this
					policy. If you choose not to provide requested details, we may be unable to deliver the full benefits of offers, competitions or services.
				</p>
				<p>
					If you no longer wish to receive marketing communications, you can unsubscribe by clicking the link in the email or emailing 
					<a class="text-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-700" href="mailto:removals@moveroo.com.au">removals@moveroo.com.au</a>. These requests are processed promptly.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">How we use and disclose information</h2>
				<p>
					Personal details you provide may include your full name, phone number, email address and service location. We also collect logistical information such as pickup & delivery addresses, vehicle details, access notes and scheduling preferences. Where relevant, we’ll ask for payment details or authorisations to complete the service.
				</p>
				<ul class="ml-6 list-disc space-y-2">
					<li>Support the functioning of the website or Moveroo business operations.</li>
					<li>Provide marketing or special offers you have opted to receive.</li>
					<li>Meet legal or regulatory obligations.</li>
					<li>Act with your express consent.</li>
				</ul>
				<p>We never sell your personal information.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Security and retention</h2>
				<p>
					We take reasonable steps to keep your personal information accurate, current and secure. While no internet transmission can be guaranteed as
					risk-free, we actively monitor and protect the systems that store your data. When personal information is no longer required, we securely destroy
					or de-identify it unless the law requires us to retain it.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Access and corrections</h2>
				<p>
					You may request access to the personal information we hold about you by emailing
					<a class="text-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-700" href="mailto:removals@moveroo.com.au">removals@moveroo.com.au</a>. If any details are inaccurate or incomplete,
					we will correct them promptly.
				</p>
				<p>
					If you need to correct or update your information, contact 
					<a class="text-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-700" href="mailto:removals@moveroo.com.au">removals@moveroo.com.au</a>. We’ll respond quickly and confirm once updates are complete.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Unsubscribing</h2>
				<p>
					To opt out of promotional emails, send a message to 
					<a class="text-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-700" href="mailto:removals@moveroo.com.au">removals@moveroo.com.au</a>
					with “UNSUBSCRIBE” in the subject line.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Updates to this policy</h2>
				<p>
					We may update this policy to reflect operational changes or regulatory updates. When material changes occur, we’ll note the revision date on this page and communicate updates through relevant channels.
					14 days before taking effect, where practical. Continuing to use the site after changes are published indicates acceptance of the updates.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Contact</h2>
				<p>
					Questions about this Privacy Policy can be directed to <a class="text-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-700" href="mailto:removals@moveroo.com.au">removals@moveroo.com.au</a>.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-6 text-base text-slate-600">
					Moveroo collects personal information that helps us provide transport estimates, coordinate logistics, comply with legal obligations and deliver services. We only request what is necessary for your booking and we handle it in accordance with the <a class="text-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-700" href="https://www.legislation.gov.au/Details/C2020C00146" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Privacy Act 1988 (Cth)</a>.
				</p>
				<p>
					To learn more about privacy rights in Australia, visit the
					<a class="text-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-700" href="https://www.oaic.gov.au" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Office of the Australian Information Commissioner</a>.
				</p>
			</section>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
